OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FShowers, possibly thundery, in
OL,6,Fthe east and southeast, especially at
OL,7,Ffirst. Rain slowly edging into
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland and western Scotland
OL,9,Flater. Sunny spells elsewhere. Still
OL,10,Fhot in the southeast, but temperatures
OL,11,Flower than of late.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA mostly warm and dry evening
OL,14,Fwith sunny spells. Clouding over from
OL,15,Fthe west with a little showery rain
OL,16,Fhere later. Dry elsewhere, remaining
OL,17,Fwarm and muggy in the east
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
