OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FCloudy for many in the morning
OL,6,Fwith a few showery outbreaks of rain.
OL,7,FTurning drier through the day with
OL,8,Fincreasing amounts of sunshine.
OL,9,FFeeling fresher than of late.
